cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 verbosity validation errors, leading to configuration rejection or undefined logging behavior.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 verbosity validation errors, leading to configuration rejection or undefined logging behavior.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致 ASN.1 詳細程度驗證錯誤，造成配置拒絕或未定義的日誌行為。
